INSERT INTO `sma_eshop_pages` (`id`, `about_us`, `contact_us`, `terms`, `p_policy`, `faq`) VALUES
(1, '<h3>About us:</h3><p><strong>Happy Feathers</strong> – \r\nOnline , Hygiene & Fresh chicken , Genuine Price.</p><p>Hello Virarkars, It’s my pleasure to introduce “Happy\r\nFeathers” to your service, A Store of one of it’s kind ,Unique in it’s nature Giving\r\nyou a happy ,Convenient & customer friendly way of buying chicken. </p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><h4>Happy feathers give you an authentic meat buying experience.\r\nyou & your loved ones can enjoy fresh & tender meat without moving out\r\nof your safe home, by placing your order through Happy Feathers Mobile App\r\n& website. </h4><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>Why\r\nHappy Feathers</strong> : </li><li>Happy\r\nFeathers came into existing with simple objective that “Every residence of\r\nVirar who loves meat should eat best quality , hygiene, tender & fresh meat\r\nwith convenient buying  experience associated\r\nwith trust.</li><li>At\r\nHappy Feathers , we are big time meat lovers so we are very choosy while\r\nserving our customers, so that you enjoy every bite of chicken on their plate.\r\nwe provide you that meat which we would like to have for us. </li><li>We\r\nunderstand the pains & inconvenience of regular chicken buyer who always have\r\nhygiene as one of the top priority. At Happy feathers we maintain high quality\r\nof hygiene & safety to make our brand trust worthy. We use Food grade\r\nstainless steel equipment / machineries at different processes i.e Cutting\r\n(halal) , Cleaning ,Storing etc. to eliminate every possible rough manhandling\r\nof Chicken.</li><li>We\r\nbring a healthy chicken from a poultry farm where they get nurtured in clean\r\nnatural atmosphere with healthy feed which is free from any chemicals, Drugs.\r\nWe use healthy chicken birds which are aged between 5-6 weeks old, which is\r\nconsidered as the best time to consume it. The chicken then gets processed, we\r\nuse traditional halal method by using sophisticated machineries for processing\r\nbirds without using any chemicals or artificial ingredients. </li><li>At\r\nHappy Feathers we are offering A to Z of chicken starts from Fresh, Tender raw\r\nchicken to Various flavors of Marinated chicken , Processed / Frozen chicken\r\nfoods i.e salami , Sausage & many other chicken related foods to ready-to-use\r\nspices (Powdered) with surety of safe delivery at your door step.</li><li>At\r\nour Airconditioned store we keep the temperature of display freeze between (0-4\r\nDeg. Cel.)  to keep the meat fresh\r\n,Tender & with nutrition maintained. A deep freezer for safe storage of\r\nProcessed & Frozen food. We use barcode while packing your meat, so you pay\r\nfor exact what you ordered. So if it looks that we charge you bit more than a\r\nregular roadside chicken shops, it just because we offers more than others\r\ngive.</li><li>As\r\nfar as freshness of happy feathers chicken is concerned, “We don’t sell which\r\nis not fresh”.&nbsp;</li></ul><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p><strong style=\"background-color: initial;\"><u>Social\r\nAwareness towards setting up Meat shops in residential areas</u></strong><strong style=\"background-color: initial;\">:</strong></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: initial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></p><ul><li>Looking\r\nat rising awareness of housing societies/Townships/complexes to decline a\r\npermit to chicken shops in their premises due to various reasons i.e from\r\nuncomfortable smells from birds & waste material to unhygienic condition of\r\nshops, considering this & keeping in mind the health of a society as a\r\npriority, we decided to keep our processing unit at nearby location where there\r\nwill not be any discomfort caused to people living around. The fresh chicken is\r\npacked in a food safe clean container then brought to store which is few\r\nhundred meters away.</li></ul><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><h4><strong>Every Happy feathers delivery contains</strong>:</h4><ul>\r\n</ul><p>&nbsp; </p><ul>\r\n<li>-Freshly packed best quality chicken /Mutton</li><li>-Hygienically handled meat</li><li>-Chemical & preservative free chicken /Mutton</li><li>-Trust of being customer centric service.&nbsp;</li></ul><h4></h4>', '<h3>\r\n Contact Us\r\n</h3><p>\r\n <strong>Email</strong>: pos@simplysafe.in</p><p>\r\n <strong>Phone</strong> :+91-7552555950</p><p>\r\n <strong>Address</strong> : H3B Nishat Enclave, 74 Bungalow</p><p>Bhopal,&nbsp;</p><p>MP 462003</p>', '<h2>TERMS AND CONDITIONS</h2><p>\r\n THESE TERMS AND CONDITIONS (\"TERMS OF USE\") IS AN ELECTRONIC RECORD IN THE FORM OF AN ELECTRONIC CONTRACT FORMED UNDER INFORMATION TECHNOLOGY ACT, 2000 AND RULES MADE THEREUNDER AND THE AMENDED PROVISIONS PERTAINING TO ELECTRONIC DOCUMENTS / RECORDS IN VARIOUS STATUTES AS AMENDED BY THE INFORMATION TECHNOLOGY ACT, 2000. THESE TERMS OF USE DOES NOT REQUIRE ANY PHYSICAL, ELECTRONIC OR DIGITAL SIGNATURE.</p><p>\r\n THESE TERMS OF USE IS A LEGALLY BINDING DOCUMENT BETWEEN USER AND COMPANY (BOTH TERMS DEFINED BELOW). THESE TERMS OF USE WILL BE EFFECTIVE UPON YOUR ACCEPTANCE OF THE SAME (DIRECTLY OR INDIRECTLY IN ELECTRONIC FORM OR BY MEANS OF AN ELECTRONIC RECORD) AND WILL GOVERN THE RELATIONSHIP BETWEEN USER AND COMPANY FOR THE USE OF THE WEBSITE (DEFINED BELOW). UPON ACCEPTANCE USER ACCEPT AND AGREE TO BE BOUND BY THESE TERMS AND CONDITIONS. COMPANY GRANTS YOU A LIMITED, NON-EXCLUSIVE, NON-TRANSFERABLE, REVOCABLE LICENCE TO USE THE SERVICES (SUBJECT TO YOUR ACCOUNT TYPE) IN ACCORDANCE WITH THESE TERMS AND CONDITIONS. ALL RIGHTS NOT EXPRESSLY GRANTED TO USERS IN THESE TERMS ARE RESERVED BY COMPANY.</p><h3>1 - TERMS</h3><p>\r\n 1.1 These terms and conditions (\"Terms and Conditions\") and all applicable Policies (as defined below) which are herein incorporated by way of reference govern your rights and obligations as an User of the Platform(s) and/or availing the services on the Platform. Any reference to \"you\" or \"User\" or \"User’s\" in these Terms and Conditions, means you the User of the Platform, browsing and/or takin