(3, 229, 'Janasya Women\'s Yellow Poly Crepe Flared Kurta', 60, 'XL', 12, 'Ritika', '2022-02-15', '3.00', 'Very good material Kurti with awsome price tag', 'A very beautiful, comfortable Kurta. I Bought suze XL and it fit me beautifully.\r\n\r\nThe material is very sturdy and looks all the more beautiful if accessorised properly.\r\n\r\nThe only Problem I felt it that crepe smells very quickly and makes you sweat in the sun!! Rest its perfect !!', NULL, 2, 0, 1, 0, NULL),
(4, 229, 'Janasya Women\'s Yellow Poly Crepe Flared Kurta', 61, '2XL', 26, 'Rupa', '2022-02-25', '2.00', 'Item received was different from item shown in picture', 'The item I received was completely different from the item shown. It was a straight long kurta. The material was not crepe. The color matched the item shown. It had an all over golden print (not just on the bodice). I returned it since it was not the style I had ordered. I am rating it 2 because the fit was decent, and the price seemed reasonable for the quality.', NULL, 3, 0, 1, 0, NULL),
