(1, 'aboutus', 'About Us', '', '<h2>About us</h2><h3>At Simply PoS (A division of Simply Safe), we all come to work every day because we have a dream of contributing towards the digital revolution in India.</h3><h4><strong>Simply PoS With its US and multiple locations in India</strong></h4><p>provides a complete solution for consumers, retailers, whole-sellers and financial institutes to connect with each other in real time through any device. This platform also opens a door to new services and Revenues for merchants.</p><p>Simply PoS platform helps  smallest of Retailers to compete in the Global and online marketplace by accepting the online orders and payments, advertising to target customers in local area and communicating with them real time on transactions.</p><h4>We are here 24*7 to understand your business needs and discuss how you can join the journey with us on the Indian Digital Highway.</h4>', 'text', 'footer_links', 0, '2021-12-23 04:38:37'),
